Title: TRESemme Platinum Strength Spray Hair Styler(Black)
Description: If Your Hair Is Regularly Exposed To Heat Either Via Styling Tools, Or The Scorching Heat Of The Sun, Then It’S Time To Protect Your Hair By Nurturing It With A Product That Can Reduce The Amount Of Damage Heat Causes To Your Hair. To Find A Permanent Solution To Thisdaily Problem, Tresemme Has Introduced A New Heat Protect Spray Suitable For All Hair Style And Types. This Spray Also Also Essential If Your Hair Has Been Recently Coloured. Styling With Heat Not Only Damages Your Hair, But It Also Strips Away Hair Colour Very Fast, Especially Shades Of Red. The Tresemme Platinum Strength Heat Protect Spray Comes In An Aesthetically Pleasing Black Bottle. It Has A Special Purple Spray Pump That Allows You To Apply It Liberally Without The Fear Of Using Too Much Product. So How Do You Use This Product? First Cleanse Your Hair By Shampooing It Thoroughly And Then Apply A Conditioner Of Your Choice. After Rinsing Out The Conditioner, Towel Dry You Hair. While It Is Still Damp, Spray The Product Along The Length Of Your Hair And Then Blow Dry Or Style As Usual. If Your Hair Is Already Dry, Or You Don’T Have The Time To Shampoo, Lightly Dampen Your Hair, And Use The Product As Mentioned Above. This Will Give You That Salon-Like Look That All Women Wish To Have. You Hair Will Be Soft, Shiny And Beautiful. So The Next Time You Think About Styling Your Hair With The Help Of A Straightening Iron, A Curling Iron, Or A Blow Dryer, Don’T Forget To Protect Your Hair By Applying This Special Hairspray.

Title: Dr. Morepen Dial Type Aneroid Sphygmomanometer BP Monitor SPG-03 Bp Monitor(Black)
Description: Dr. Morepen SPG03 Aneroid Blood Pressure Monitor is a leading name in the segment of hospital apparatus and medical calibration tools used to measure blood pressure. The Aneroid Blood Pressure Monitor consists of an inflatable cuff wrapped around the arms to restrict the blood flow. The blood pressure is calibrated over a circular dial to hint the maximum and minimum pressure. Unlike traditional sphygmomanometers, the Dr. Morepen SPG03 Aneroid Blood Pressure Monitor is completely mercury free and used with manual pump and connected to a stethoscope to heart beats of the heart.Aneroid Blood Pressure Monitors from Dr. Morepen have mechanism for calibration checks with reasonable accuracy. Dr. Morepen SPG03 Aneroid Blood Pressure Monitor has a provision for mounting on walls and stands to negate the effects of calibration errors. The entire cardiac cycle can be observed using the Aneroid Blood Pressure Monitor. The control valve maintains the pressure and the dial reflects the value in mm/Hg. Governed by the principle of Auscultatory method, the calibration highlights the anomalies in the five phases associated with cardiac function.

Title: Majik Auburn Hair Building Fiber(7 grams) With Optimizer Comb(Set of)
Description: Hair loss is a very common problem that number of people suffer from. There are number of products available in the market to prevent this problem. If you are suffering from a drastic hair fall and partial baldness, you could opt for Hair Building Fiber by Majik. Majik is a Swiss based brand which is recognized as one of the most reputed hair-care brands all over the world. From the Manufacturer What It Is Majik Hair Building Fibers, made of 100% Human hair, blend undetectably with existing hair strands to instantly create the appearance of naturally thick and full hair. What It Does Instantly fills in thinning areas Conceals hair loss Makes fine hair look completely thick and full Great as a root touch-up between colorings What Else You Need To Know Majik Hair Fibers resist wind, rain, and perspiration for long lasting results in all conditions. Available in nine shades that can be mixed to match Indian hair color, Hair Fibers work for all hair types and textures. Also great for part lines, covering extension tracks and touching up roots between hair color appointments. Easily washes out with shampoo. How to Apply Dry and style hair as usual. Shake Hair Fibers into thinning areas. If applying Hair Fibers near the hairline, use Majik Hairline Optimizer to achieve a natural looking front hairline. Gently pat hair to disperse Hair Fibers. If desired, lightly comb, brush, or style your hair after applying Hair Fibers. For best results, use Majik Hair Fiber Spray to finish for longer-lasting results.

Title: DèVe Herbes Wintergreen Essential Oil - Pack Of Two (100ml + 100ml) Gaultheria Procumbens
Description: Wintergreen essential oil 100+100ml: Wintergreen essential oil has a strong and cooling aroma. It invokes awareness and concentration as well as having many physical benefits. Wintergreen essential oil contains 85-99% of methyl salicylate, the same component of aspirin. 30 ml of wintergreen oil is equivalent to about 171 adult aspirin tablets or about 60 grams of aspirin. Birch and wintergreen are the only plants in the world that naturally contain methyl salicylate. It is documented that these oils have cortisone-like effects that can relieve pain quickly. Birch and wintergreen were considered the best essential oils for pain before synthetics were made in the early 1920s. Title: Salve Hairvital Shampoo Pack of 3(200 ml)
Description: Ingredients : Aloe Vera, Wheat Germ Protein, Jojoba Oil, Vitamin E Hairvital shampoo contains everything your hair wants Moisturizers: Glycerin, Sorbitol , Cocoamidopropyl Betaine. Glycerin helps to maintain moisture. It prevents hair fall & also acts an an anti-ageing. element. It prevents hair from getting dry and thus avoids dandruff. Sorbitol maintains moisture in hair and keeps your hair smooth, soft, shiny and lustrous. Cocamidopropyl betaine is a humectant, attracting moisture from the air, thus keeping hair from drying out. Reconstructors: Hydrolysed Wheat Protein -is a leading source of vitamins & essential amino acids. It is an excellent hydrator, readily absorbed by the skin for improved texture & resilience. It combines with fatty acids & amino acids to coat porous or damaged hair & help repair split-ends. A unique BI-Phase formula containing cleanser & conditioner in the same bottle. How Hairvital works, (1) surfactant molecules and conditioner particles surround the hair, each conditioner particle is suspended inside a separate cage. The surfactant molecules are attracted to the dirt on the hair and lift it away leaving the hair clean. At the time of rinsing the conditioner particles are released from the cage and because of their electrical charge they cling to the clean hair. Detanglers: Polyquaternium-10, Cetrimonium chloride. Is a complex, cationic polymeric conditioning agent derived from, wood cellulose. Provides body while it improves curl bounce and adds fullness to the hair. It further improves wet and dry combing, detangling, & imparts sheen, adding a silky feel to the hair. Cetrimonium chloride is used as a hair conditioner. Thermal protectors and Glossers: Silicone Oil Thermal protectors, usually heat-absorbing polymers, shielding the hair against excessive heat, caused by, e.g., blow-drying or curling irons or hot rollers. Light-reflecting chemicals which bind to the hair surface. Oils: Wheat Germ oil, Jojoba Oil Oils (EFAs - essential fatty acids), help dry/porous hair to become more soft and pliable. The scalp produces a natural oil called sebum. EFAs are the closest thing to natural sebum (sebum contains EFAs). Wheat germ oil, a skin nourisher contains high levels of Vitamin E oil as well as other vitamins, minerals, protein & Essential Fatty Acids. Jojoba Oil creates a protective film over the hair shaft that helps keep moisture in. Highly effective on dry or sundamaged hair. Jojoba oil is composed of liquid wax esters which make up 26-30% of our skin's surface layer called sebum, the oily substance responsible for giving a smooth effect to hair. Surfactants: Sodium Lauryl Ether Sulphate, Cocodiethanolamide, PEG-7 Glycerylcocoate. Hair consists of approximately 97% of a protein called keratin. The surface of keratin contains negatively-charged amino acids. Hair conditioners therefore usually contain cationic surfactants, which don't wash out completely, because their hydrophilic ends strongly bind to keratin. The hydrophobic ends of the surfactant molecules then act as the new hair surface. Sodium Lauryl Ether sulfate. Is derived from coconut; it is used primarily as a detergent cleansing agent. It is considered gentle and effective. Cocodiethanolamide is used as a foam stabilizing agent. It is also a viscosity booster. Lubricants: Simeticone Oil Sequestrants: Ethylenediaminetetraacetic acid Sodium. Ethylenediaminetetraacetic acid Sodium, prevent ingredients from binding with trace elements (particularly minerals) that can exist in water and with other ingredients to cause unwanted product changes to the texture, the odor, and the consistency. Multifunctional Agent : Peg 7 Peg 7 has excellent emulsifying, emollient, refatting & thickening properties, useful as surfactant with good conditioning effect for soft & smooth skin/hair.

Title: Rejsol Glycolic Acid Peel 40% 50 ml with 100 Neutralizer, Pre Peeling Cleanser, Moisturizer , Sunscreen.(750 ml)
Description: Glycolic Acid is Peeling agent that removes the superficial Dead skin layer and causes growth of new lighter glowing skin.Chemical Peels are acids therefore should be used under the Supervision of trained cosmetologists.Always do Patch Test when using the peel for the first time.Patch test: Apply small amount of peel below neck or armpit, see for any redness beyond the margin of application, if seendiscontinue the procedure. If no redness or itching continue with the procedureProcedure:Cleanse the skin with oil free cleanser, if using oil containing cleanser, after cleansing whip with alcohol or spirit. oil blocks the acid therefore desired action is not achieved.Apply Peel with brush or ear Buds, gel peels can be best applied with gloved fingers. start applying from the forehead upto the neck, application time should not be more than 20 seconds. keep peel for 3-7 mins depending on your skin habituality of peeling and the peel strength. Spray neutralizer, keep for 1 min.wash with water., apply sunscreen and good moisturiser for 7 days twice daily.Post Peel:Success of the peeling depends on sunprotection and moisturisingfirst the skin dies so becomes black don't worry this is the skin that is going to peel of itselfThere are two types of peeling microscopic that is not seen by naked eyes, and macroscopic peeling that is visualised very wellDo not remove the skin by your self.Don't use soap for 2-3 days, thereafter, use mild soap for 7-8 days, don't scrub too hardNote: If you don't get desired results doesnt mean the peel is not working it only means that your skin is tough for the peel you are using. then its time to use stronger peels or increase the application time of the peel in the next sitting.
